Package main.java.GUINew

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CaGuiPrototype
    User Interface for Cryptanalysis components.
    ComponentLinker
    Draws the lines that illustrate which letters are linked together in the plugboard.
    ConfigureOutput
    Class to format the input for processing.
    EnigmaGUI
    Driver/outer GUI to contain and organize the Enigma GUI elements.
    EnigmaSingleton
    Uses the Singleton and Observer design patterns to enable data sharing across the various modular GUI pieces.
    IOPanel
    Combines all of the IO functionality of the Enigma, providing ways to encrypt characters, long strings, and entire files.
    Lightboard
    Provides a visual "Light Board" display of the last output character following encryption.
    PlugboardDialog
    PlugBoard dialog window pop-up for character pair selection.
    ResetPanel
    Encapsulates the functionality to reset the machine state in one of three different ways.
    ResultsPanel
    Panel which displays the results of Cryptanalysis.
    RotorPanel
    Top panel of the modular GUI for the Enigma Machine.
